And we're actually committed
to keeping that open source

00:20:31.490 --> 00:20:33.040
and continuing to innovate
on that.

00:20:33.040 --> 00:20:34.150
And we've got some
more open source

00:20:34.150 --> 00:20:35.880
libraries coming up soon.

00:20:35.880 --> 00:20:38.370
We use a compatibility library,
fragments, loaders,

00:20:38.370 --> 00:20:38.940
all that stuff.

00:20:38.940 --> 00:20:41.560
So no matter what Android phone
you're on, it's going to

00:20:41.560 --> 00:20:44.340
look exactly the same and
provide a consistent user

00:20:44.340 --> 00:20:45.230
experience.

00:20:45.230 --> 00:20:46.610
So that is Pay With Square.

00:20:46.610 --> 00:20:48.036
Thank you.

