00:51:40.490 --> 00:51:42.700
button color, but we didn't
tweak the text color.

00:51:42.700 --> 00:51:45.170
So we ended up with
white on white.

00:51:45.170 --> 00:51:48.030
So once you start messing with
customizations in the theme,

00:51:48.030 --> 00:51:49.890
you pretty much have to
customize everything.

00:51:49.890 --> 00:51:53.210
