just by clicking from

01:17:04.355 --> 01:17:05.740
the action bar.

01:17:05.740 --> 01:17:09.120
But definitely adding more
gestures to be able to

01:17:09.120 --> 01:17:11.940
navigate around the rest
of the app as well.

