all those actions on the

01:17:59.490 --> 01:18:00.310
action bar?

01:18:00.310 --> 01:18:01.450
Again, how we can
bring gestures.

01:18:01.450 --> 01:18:03.130
How can we innovate
with gestures?

01:18:03.130 --> 01:18:05.700
I think the reason why we
selected the Papyrus

01:18:05.700 --> 01:18:08.080
