Sergey's picture in there.

02:00:49.280 --> 02:00:51.200
And Facebook, I can see how that
could be useful, though

02:00:51.200 --> 02:00:53.270
of course I'm a Google+ user,
so I don't know what this

02:00:53.270 --> 02:00:54.440
Facebook thing is.

02:00:54.440 --> 02:00:55.690
But--

02:00:57.880 --> 02:00:59.130
RICHARD FULCHER: So much
smarter than me.

